'''Assia Mutoni''' ni Umunya[[rwanda]]<nowiki/>zi wavutse 14, Nyakanga 1993, wamenyekanye nka Rosine muri filimi yakunzwe cyane "Intare y'ingore"<ref>https://igihe.com/imyidagaduro/article/assia-mutoni-ntakitabiriye-iserukiramuco-rya-sinema-rikomeye-yatumiwemo-muri</ref>, Ni umwanditsi akaba n'umukinnyi wa filimi nyarwanda guhera muri 2012<ref>https://umuryango.rw/ad-restricted/article/reba-amafoto-ya-mutoni-assia-ufatwa-nk-ikizungerezi-muri-cinema-nyarwanda-mu</ref>. ubu amaze gutsindira ibihembo inshuro 8 bitangwa nabahemba abakinnyi ba filimi bitwaye neza <ref>https://www.newtimes.co.rw/entertainment/wedding-dress-assia-mutonis-movie-compete-international-film-festival</ref>, zimwe muri filimi amaze gukinamo ni City Maid, Intare y'Ingore, Seburikoko, Impeta Yanjye, Giramata nizindi<ref>http://www.isimbi.rw/imyidagaduro/article/assia-mutoni-yavuze-igihe-azagira-muri-amerika</ref>.<ref>https://mni.rw/CompetitionVote/501</ref>

== Ubuzima bwa Assia muri make ==
Assia yavukiye i [[Akarere ka Nyamagabe|Nyamagabe]] gusa iwabo bimukira I [[Kigali]] afite umwaka umwe gusa, amashuri abanza yayize kuri Remera Catholic primary school, ayisumbuye ayiga Lycee de Nyanza na RHC Gasogi aharangiza muri 2012 ,Kaminuza ayiga muri UTB mu bijyanye n'Ubukerarugendo aharangiza muri 2016<ref>https://m.eachamps.rw/article/2910/Mutoni-Assia-Rosine-yihakanye--Mico-The-Best-ashyira-hanze-umukunzi-we--amafoto</ref><ref>https://m.eachamps.rw/article/3617/Mutoni-Assia-Rosine-arayoboye-mu-majwi-yabahatanira-Rwanda-Movie-Awards-kuri-Internet</ref>. Yatangiye gukina filimi muri 2012 , filimi yahereyeho harimo Rwema, Ntundekure ariko iyatumye amenyekana ni Intare y'Ingore muri 2015 aho yatumye  atwara igihembo cy'umukinnyi w'umukobwa watowe nabantu benshi muri 2016<ref>https://ibicu.com/mutoni-assia-yeruye-ahishura-ko-amaze-kurya-amafaranga-yabagabo-atazi-umubare-wabo/
</ref><ref>https://ar.umuseke.rw/filime-zo-hanze-ntizigifite-isoko-mu-rwanda-nka-mbere-mutoni-assia.hmtl</ref>. Muri 2021 akaba yaratoranyijwe mubakinnyi bazitabira iserukiramuco Silicon Valley African Film festival ribera muri [[Amerika]]<ref>https://inyarwanda.com/inkuru/108330/amarangamutima-ya-mutoni-assia-nyuma-yuko-firime-ye-wedding-dress-itoranyijwe-mu-iserukira-108330.html</ref>..

